02:12:02.709 --> 02:12:18.079
This popped out to me today because the Lord said, 'I had Deuteronomy 28 playing on my phone, and I paused it when I got to that verse,'and He said, 'long duration.'Do you get that?

02:12:18.080 --> 02:12:27.319
Sicknesses of long duration, great plagues of long continuance.

02:12:27.320 --> 02:12:36.390
I said, 'Well, Lord, tell my people this is scripture they can stand on.

02:12:36.391 --> 02:12:42.199
You've got COVID for a long time? You've got symptoms that have never left you?

02:12:42.200 --> 02:12:59.119
Christ has redeemed you from that.'Did I help somebody? I thought that was pretty good. I got blessed by it.

02:12:59.120 --> 02:13:11.463
It says great plagues of long continuance and sores and sicknesses of long continuance.

02:13:11.464 --> 02:13:31.319
It means it's happened a long time, and He's redeemed us from it according to Galatians 3.

02:13:31.320 --> 02:13:43.123
So if you like it, latch onto it. It's something for you to stand on. Father, I thank You for creative ideas to get wealth.

02:13:43.124 --> 02:13:53.199
Thank You, Lord, that as we start out March, when we get to the 31st, we're going to have a supernatural breakthrough.

02:13:53.200 --> 02:14:14.139
I contend and lay hold to what we've been believing for. What we believe for the third month of 2026, we will have it in full before the end of the first quarter.

02:14:14.140 --> 02:14:31.705
Remember, He said, 'Believe Me for the first quarter for the whole year's budget.'For everything you're believing for, this is it—to have the abundant supply for the rest of the year, for debt to be paid off, to live in the overflow.

02:14:31.706 --> 02:14:42.994
Latch onto it and believe God for bigger. We're in the first quarter, and it's almost over.

02:14:42.995 --> 02:14:53.875
March 1st, we're believing for an expiration date for what we've been believing for. Today is the day of a turnaround. Thank You, Lord.

02:14:53.876 --> 02:15:03.719
By the 31st of this month, we call for exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

02:15:03.720 --> 02:15:15.799
Your boss is going to call you and say, 'Hey, I want to give you a raise.'Maybe if you're in the United States and you file your taxes, you'll get a return; you won't owe.

02:15:15.800 --> 02:15:31.752
Let's believe God for abundance. 'Well, I always owe, brother. I have to write a check to the IRS every year.'Not this year!

02:15:31.753 --> 02:15:37.999
This year, you're going to believe God for increase, for a return.

02:15:38.000 --> 02:15:58.979
Why not believe God for favor? There might be some kind of new law or something. I always believe for something positive.

02:15:58.980 --> 02:16:11.374
Either way, you're believing for something—the good or the bad—so I'm leaning for good.

02:16:11.375 --> 02:16:17.319
Whatever things you desire when you pray, believe that you receive them, and you shall have them.

02:16:17.320 --> 02:16:25.193
What are you saying out of your mouth? 'I'm debt-free. I have more than enough.

02:16:25.194 --> 02:16:34.439
My storehouse is in overflow.'Well, if you keep saying you're barely getting by, you're going to keep living it.

02:16:34.440 --> 02:16:45.894
I'm going to say what I'm believing for. March is here and I'm excited. I told Diana, 'Let's get excited.

02:16:45.895 --> 02:16:55.834
What are we believing for?'We left February—it wasn't the best month—but I said, 'Shake it off.

02:16:55.835 --> 02:17:04.666
Let's go. March is here.'We talked about it this morning during prayer and communion.

02:17:04.667 --> 02:17:10.756
It's time to believe God. We got COVID in February, and she got real sick.

02:17:10.757 --> 02:17:19.319
She couldn't smell or taste for over a week and a half, but she's feeling so good today.

02:17:19.320 --> 02:17:31.839
Thank You, Lord. I'm going to read the blessings, and then you can go if you want to.

02:17:31.840 --> 02:17:45.558
But I feel sometimes you all need hope. Take this into your week and meditate on something bigger than yourself.

02:17:45.559 --> 02:17:52.159
If you can do it on your own, it's not big enough. You're not thinking big enough.

02:17:52.160 --> 02:18:01.756
You've got to get God out of your box and stop trying to make him into—well, it has to be about my 8 to 5 Monday through Friday for him to find.

02:18:01.757 --> 02:18:12.833
If you can do it and achieve it, you're not believing big enough. It has to be outside of your realm. How?

02:18:12.834 --> 02:18:20.619
It's not going to happen by me; it's going to have to happen from a supernatural God with signs.

02:18:20.620 --> 02:18:25.718
He said, 'I want to show you signs.'This is it. Think big. This is big.

02:18:25.719 --> 02:18:33.933
Okay. Blessed shall be the basket and your kneading trough.

02:18:33.934 --> 02:18:40.512
Blessed shall you be when you come in, and blessed shall you be when you go out.

02:18:40.513 --> 02:18:49.759
The Lord shall cause your enemies who rise up against you to be defeated before your face.

02:18:49.760 --> 02:18:54.638
They shall come out against you one way and flee before you seven ways.

02:18:54.639 --> 02:19:12.319
The Lord shall command the blessing upon you and your storehouse and in all that you undertake, and he will bless you in the land which the Lord your God gives you.

02:19:12.320 --> 02:19:37.197
The Lord will establish you as a people holy to himself, as he has sworn to you, if you keep the commandments of the Lord your God and walk in his ways, and all the people of the earth will see that you are called by the name and in the presence of the Lord.

02:19:37.198 --> 02:19:44.164
I love that. I just love that you're called in the name and in the presence.

02:19:44.165 --> 02:20:26.199
As Billy said last night when I was on the phone with him, he said, 'There's so many you can walk up to and shake their hand and there's no presence that are big names.'He never mentions names, but he said, 'But I can go to a little old lady in the back that has a relationship with Jesus, and the moment I shake her hand, I feel the presence.'When he said that, I thought, the little old lady in the back has more presence than some big preachers that pretend they do.

02:20:26.200 --> 02:20:45.519
Why? Maybe she got a hold of Deuteronomy. And the people of the earth shall see that you are called by the name and in the presence of the Lord, and they shall be afraid of you.

02:20:45.520 --> 02:20:56.839
And the Lord shall make you have a surplus of prosperity through the fruit of your body.

02:20:56.840 --> 02:21:06.759
Now, I don't know what surplus means to you, but a surplus to me is more than just having my bills paid for March.

02:21:06.760 --> 02:21:19.293
Well, I'm excited about it, and I give God praise for the electric, gas, water, phone, your internet, your car payment, and your car insurance, and you're so grateful for it.

02:21:19.294 --> 02:21:30.999
But that's not surplus. So he said right here, 'And the Lord shall make you have a surplus.'So I'm not going to miss out on that.

02:21:31.000 --> 02:21:38.879
I'm going to believe for it. Of prosperity through the fruit of your body. That means my kids are blessed.

02:21:38.880 --> 02:21:43.559
And of your livestock—which I don't do, like, that's YouTube and eBay and Poshmark.

02:21:43.560 --> 02:21:49.556
And the fruit of your body and in the livestock and in the ground, in the land which the Lord swore to your fathers to give you.

02:21:49.557 --> 02:21:56.726
So I believe for inheritance. So if I have to believe for inheritance, that means my family—mom and dad—have to be blessed.

02:21:56.727 --> 02:22:03.832
Somebody has to be blessed because they can't leave you anything.

02:22:03.833 --> 02:22:09.239
If they don't have anything to leave you, that is an inheritance.

02:22:09.240 --> 02:22:17.262
So believe in God for others around you. It's not just about yourself. So you believe for people that are your extended family.

02:22:17.263 --> 02:22:23.239
You say, 'Listen, I'm believing God for them to be blessed because if the Lord tarries, they're going to go home by the graveside.'And guess what?

02:22:23.240 --> 02:22:35.679
You don't want them to be leaving debt and being broke and busted and disgusted. So they got to have a surplus. It's generational, right?

02:22:35.680 --> 02:22:44.474
I want if the Lord tarries and I go home by the graveside—which I don't believe he will, but if he did—I want my son to be blessed.

02:22:44.475 --> 02:22:51.605
You don't want to go home and him go, 'Well, dad left me a lot of debt and all this stuff that he had, all these bills and all, look at what happened.'No, no.

02:22:51.606 --> 02:22:59.248
Dad left me a surplus. Why? Because it's abundance. God's a God of abundance.

02:22:59.249 --> 02:23:06.434
And so many people get ticked off about this, but I believe it. I believe it.

02:23:06.435 --> 02:23:10.959
Deuteronomy 28, that's Old Testament, but I still believe it.

02:23:10.960 --> 02:23:23.959
I'm applying myself to it. Why not believe God for it? What's wrong with that?

02:23:23.960 --> 02:23:30.279
You got stinking thinking. Don't have stinking thinking. Surplus.

02:23:30.280 --> 02:23:36.374
The fruit of your body and the livestock and in your ground in a land which the Lord swore to your fathers to give you.

02:23:36.375 --> 02:23:43.756
The Lord shall open to you his good treasures: the heavens to give the rain on your land in a season, and to bless all the work of your hand.

02:23:43.757 --> 02:23:48.959
And you shall lend unto many nations, and you shall not borrow.

02:23:48.960 --> 02:23:56.079
And the Lord shall make you the head and not the tail, and you shall be above only, and you shall not be beneath.

02:23:56.080 --> 02:24:03.085
If you heed the commandments of the Lord your God, which I am commanding you this day, and are watchful to do them.

02:24:03.086 --> 02:24:08.999
I'm going to follow him. Love the Lord my God with all my heart, mind, soul, and strength, and love your neighbor as yourself.

02:24:09.000 --> 02:24:24.279
Did you give him that? Look at him. That's Putin in the count. That's creepy bee. That's what he looked like.

02:24:24.280 --> 02:24:28.159
So, I'm just trying to encourage you to believe God for your March.

02:24:28.160 --> 02:24:33.239
Go into this month expecting God to show up and show off in your life.

02:24:33.240 --> 02:24:36.839
You're believing for a baby? This is your month to conceive a baby.

02:24:36.840 --> 02:24:41.306
You're believing for a spouse? This is your month to find your spouse.

02:24:41.307 --> 02:24:47.736
What if you say, 'Well, I'm going to find the man of my dreams this month,'or the woman of my dreams.

02:24:47.737 --> 02:24:55.420
You go, 'Hey, I'm going to find my diamond in the rough. This is my month.'Why not believe?

02:24:55.421 --> 02:24:57.935
I'm not going to be alone any month. I'm going to find somebody.

02:24:57.936 --> 02:25:04.220
God's going to bring me a spouse. You may not get married this month, but at least you find them.

02:25:04.221 --> 02:25:09.159
Don't freak her out and say, 'I'm going to propose to you. I found you.

02:25:09.160 --> 02:25:18.599
Here she is. Let's propose.'You'll freak her out. She'd run the other way. This guy's too aggressive.

02:25:18.600 --> 02:25:26.759
'I've been waiting for you.'The woman's going, 'I've already got my wedding dress picked out, sir.

02:25:26.760 --> 02:25:34.314
Don't worry. I'm waiting at the altar.'And he's like, 'I just met you yesterday, lady.'Don't be that way.

02:25:34.315 --> 02:25:39.228
You'll freak him out. She isn't going like this, 'Oh, I'm ready.

02:25:39.229 --> 02:25:54.079
I got the cake picked out and the kids'names.'You're going to scare him. Don't do that. He'll run.

02:25:54.080 --> 02:25:57.356
Even if you're believing for him, that could be your perfect spouse and God brought him.

02:25:57.357 --> 02:26:15.279
You scare him off. Go low, go slow. Nice to meet you first. Let's have a cup of coffee. Don't talk wedding plans on the first date, ladies.

02:26:15.280 --> 02:26:30.039
I try to cut up with you a little bit, but I'm going to tell y'all: believe God for big things for the month of March.

02:26:30.040 --> 02:26:36.080
Reach out and if you can achieve it, you're not believing big enough.

02:26:36.081 --> 02:26:43.839
It's going to take a supernatural God to bring supernatural things to you. Don't just believe for the status quo.

02:26:43.840 --> 02:26:48.399
Believe exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think for the month of March.

02:26:48.400 --> 02:26:53.245
And remember, the seed you sowed in the past will come to harvest at last.

02:26:53.246 --> 02:26:59.519
The Lord said to believe for 30, 60, and 100-fold over what you've been sowing.

02:26:59.520 --> 02:27:12.919
What you gave to the church, wherever you're attending, believe for those seeds to come back.

02:27:12.920 --> 02:27:18.788
Don't allow the devil to be robbing you of your fruit. Stand.

02:27:18.789 --> 02:27:28.834
But you got to contend for it using the word of God, putting it in your heart and keeping him the main thing.

02:27:28.835 --> 02:27:34.799
Seek ye first the kingdom and all these things will be added unto you. Seek them. Use the word.

02:27:34.800 --> 02:27:41.278
So, I hope that blessed you because I was thinking about March 1st today. What are we believing for?

02:27:41.279 --> 02:27:55.279
What are Diana and I believing for, stretching your capacity and your ability to believe Him for more?

02:27:55.280 --> 02:27:58.046
Some ministries say, "Well, I'm believing for this and that."No, no.

02:27:58.047 --> 02:28:02.799
It's time to believe God for bigger. Why? Because we're running out of time.

02:28:02.800 --> 02:28:08.998
The wealth of the sinner is laid up for the righteous. What's that? I don't know.

