02:28:29.200 --> 02:28:37.236
I told you Israel—the Lord wouldn't allow me to say—remember the night a couple, what was it, three or four nights ago?

02:28:37.237 --> 02:28:43.047
I went in the spirit about Israel's weapons and I saw some things that I told Braden.

