I tried to—Turkey is—is that the only waterway that leads to the Black Sea? Yeah, I think so.

02:30:37.840 --> 02:30:49.199
We usually study this stuff on our own, you know, afterwards, but it's after the Lord tells us what's happening.

02:30:49.200 --> 02:30:53.839
The Black Sea. And there looks like several passages there.

02:30:53.840 --> 02:31:04.750
Three different passages. Yeah, it's called the Istanbul Canal. So, we love y'all.

02:31:04.751 --> 02:31:13.180
Thank you for joining us tonight and I'm so excited for all the salvations that we had. 63 people gave their heart to Jesus Christ and we love you.

02:31:13.181 --> 02:31:17.960
I know it's a long—I've been here two and a half hours, so we've prayed quite a while tonight.

02:31:17.961 --> 02:31:23.614
I appreciate all of you. Is that really 9,000 still here? No.

02:31:23.615 --> 02:31:29.097
Oh, I was going to say, wow, that's incredible. If they're still here after that, 7,000.

02:31:29.098 --> 02:31:39.238
