02:31:39.239 --> 02:31:49.467
And we'll go over things we saw again today and tomorrow, and I'll tell you more of what I saw and bring it more to light.

02:31:49.468 --> 02:31:56.800
We appreciate you being here. God bless y'all. Love you. Bye-bye.

